# Tech Stack

- Supabase (PostgreSQL, Auth, Realtime, Edge Functions).
- Python (FastAPI or lightweight scripts for AI/ML).
- Infrastructure: Dockerized applications optimized for deployment on Dokploy.

# Database & Security Rules

- Always use `snake_case` for PostgreSQL database columns and tables.
- Always implement Row Level Security (RLS) in Supabase queries. Workers should only see their own policies and claims.
- Never expose Supabase service role keys on the client side.

# AI & Edge Function Logic

- Edge Functions (Deno) should be used as webhooks to receive third-party API triggers (e.g., Tomorrow.io) and insert records into the `claims` table.
- Python scripts should handle the dynamic Weekly premium calculations and anomaly/fraud detection models.
